	<key>readme</key>
	<string>Universal Converter for Alfred

Keywords: c, ct, cc

Convert (c):
  c 12pm to pdt      — timezone conversion
  c 1000 krw to usd  — currency conversion

Timezone Dashboard (ct):
  ct              — current time in saved timezones
  ct 10am         — convert time to saved timezones
  ct add tokyo    — add a timezone
  ct remove tokyo — remove a timezone

Currency Dashboard (cc):
  cc              — rates for saved currencies
  cc 1000         — convert amount to saved currencies
  cc add usd      — add a currency
  cc remove eur   — remove a currency

Press Enter to copy result or add/remove.</string>
